Create a recorder event, when the MediaService is not known, but the terminal is. Author: Richard Deadman
Parameters:
evId - The Symbol that represents the event according to the ECTF.
termName - The name of the terminal the event's MediaService is associated with.
err - The Symbol that represents the error, or null.
qual - Additional information about why an event occured, such as q_Duration.
trigger - The RTC trigger that caused the event.
duration - The number of milliseconds in a completed recording.
